Notes: NCAA Division III Second Round game...SP snaps WU's 36-game winning streak and
70-game home winning streak...WU had won four straight Division III titles and
20 straight NCAA games...SP led 17-16 with 5:55 left in first half and went on
13-1 run, hitting four straight three-pointers...SP led entire second half.
Game.Officials: Ken Thaxton,  Barb Fagan,  John Thomas
